(17416, 'Cipramaline 10 mg 20 f.c. tabs.', 'سيبرامالين 10مجم 20 قرص', '110', '144', 'Escitalopram', 'Medisen pharmaceutical industries', 'Tab', 'أقراص', 'لاج الاضطراب الاكتئابي الرئيسي واضطراب الوسواس القهري واضطراب ما بعد الصدمة واضطراب الهلع', 'Psychiatric.antidepressants', '10 mg', 'Escitalopram is indicated for the acute and maintenance treatment of major depressive disorder (MDD) in adults and pediatric patients 12 years old and older and for the acute treatment of generalized anxiety disorder (GAD) in adults and pediatric patients 7 years old and older.[L8513,L8513] It is additionally indicated for symptomatic relief of obsessive-compulsive disorder (OCD) in Canada.[L8516]', '6225000349728', '', 4547, '2024-10-28', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
